                <head>No. 661<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For documentation concerning the Nine-Power and Four-Power Conferences at London,
                    September 28–October 3, 1954, see <ref target="frus1952-54v05p2#pg_1294">volume
                        V, Part 2, pages 1294</ref> ff. Included in that compilation is a record of
                        <pb facs="0362" n="1452" xml:id="pg_1452"/> all the formal Nine-Power and
                    Four-Power meetings as well as the bipartite meetings between the United States
                    and French officials and tripartite meetings which also included the
                    British.</p>
            </div>
